<li id="cite_note-MINOSlv-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-MINOSlv_27-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">MINOS Collaboration, P. Adamson et al., <i>Testing Lorentz Invariance and CPT Conservation with NuMI Neutrinos in the MINOS Near Detector</i>, Phys. Rev. Lett. 101, 151601 (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/0806.4945">arXiv:0806.4945</a></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">MINOS Collaboration, P. Adamson et al., <i>Search for Lorentz invariance and CPT violation with muon antineutrinos in the MINOS Near Detector</i>, Phys. Rev. D 85, 031101 (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1201.2631">arXiv:1201.2631</a></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-MB_LV-29"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-MB_LV_29-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">MiniBooNE Collaboration, T. Katori, <i>Test for Lorentz and CPT Violation with the MiniBooNE Low-Energy Excess</i>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1008.0906">arXiv:1008.0906</a>.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">MiniBooNE Collaboration, A.A. Aguilar-Arevalo, <i>Test of Lorentz and CPT violation with Short Baseline Neutrino Oscillation Excesses</i>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1109.3480">arXiv:1109.3480</a>.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-IceCube_LV-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-IceCube_LV_31-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">IceCube Collaboration, R. Abbasi et al., <i>Search for a Lorentz-violating sidereal signal with atmospheric neutrinos in IceCube</i>, Phys. Rev. D 82, 112003 (2010). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1010.4096">arXiv:1010.4096</a>.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-12.DataTables-32"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-12.DataTables_32-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-12.DataTables_32-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation journal">Kostelecky, V.A.; Russell, N. (2010). "Data Tables for Lorentz and CPT Violation". <i><a href="/wiki/Reviews_of_Modern_Physics" title="Reviews of Modern Physics">Reviews of Modern Physics</a></i> <b>83</b>: 11. <a href="/wiki/ArXiv" title="ArXiv">arXiv</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//arxiv.org/abs/0801.0287">0801.0287</a>. <a href="/wiki/Bibcode" title="Bibcode">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2011RvMP...83...11K">2011RvMP...83...11K</a>. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//dx.doi.org/10.1103%2FRevModPhys.83.11">10.1103/RevModPhys.83.11</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALorentz-violating+neutrino+oscillations&amp;rft.atitle=Data+Tables+for+Lorentz+and+CPT+Violation&amp;rft.aufirst=V.A.&amp;rft.au=Kostelecky%2C+V.A.&amp;rft.aulast=Kostelecky&amp;rft.au=Russell%2C+N.&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=info%3Aarxiv%2F0801.0287&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2011RvMP...83...11K&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1103%2FRevModPhys.83.11&amp;rft.jtitle=Reviews+of+Modern+Physics&amp;rft.pages=11&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=83" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-DKM-33"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-DKM_33-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-DKM_33-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">J.S. Diaz, V.A. Kostelecky, and M. Mewes, <i>Perturbative Lorentz and CPT violation for neutrino and antineutrino oscillations</i>, Phys. Rev. D 80, 076007 (2009). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/0908.1401">arXiv:0908.1401</a></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-MINOS_LV2-34"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-MINOS_LV2_34-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">MINOS Collaboration, P. Adamson et al., <i>A Search for Lorentz Invariance and CPT Violation with the MINOS Far Detector</i>, Phys. Rev. Lett. 105, 151601 (2010). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1007.2791">arXiv:1007.2791</a>.</span></li>
